<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12">
    <h1>Please Check Your Email</h1>
    <p>You're just a few short steps from completing the signup process!  We sent an email to <%= @person&.email %>.  Please click the link in that message to verify
    your email address and continue the signup process.</p>
    <p>If you don't see the email in your inbox, please check your spam folder.</p>
    <p>If you don't receive the email within a few minutes, please <%= link_to 'reset your password', new_password_reset_path %> to continue.</p>
  </div>
</div>
